OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784710094
OL,3,CFirefighters scrambled to huge
OL,4,Cwoodland blaze in Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FA large woodland fire has broken out
OL,7,Fin Macclesfield Forest, Cheshire Fire
OL,8,Fand Rescue Service has confirmed.
OL,10,FMembers of the public have been urged
OL,11,Fto stay away as firefighters attempt
OL,12,Fto get the fire under control. Six
OL,13,Ffire engines have already been
OL,14,Fdispatched and more are on the way to
OL,15,Fwoodland near Hacked Way Lane.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
