OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784710094
OL,3,CFirefighters scrambled to huge
OL,4,Cwoodland blaze in Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,FIn a statement this evening, the fire
OL,7,Fservice said: "Firefighters are
OL,8,Fcurrently dealing with a large
OL,9,Fwoodland and grass fire in
OL,10,FMacclesfield Forest. Crews are at the
OL,11,Fscene tackling the blaze, with
OL,12,Fadditional resources on their way to
OL,13,Fassist. Members of the public are
OL,14,Furged to avoid the area while
OL,15,Femergency services work to bring the
OL,16,Ffire under control.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
