PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784710094
OL,3,CFirefighters scrambled to huge
OL,4,Cwoodland blaze in Macclesfield Forest
OL,6,F"Smoke may be visible from surrounding
OL,7,Fareas and people nearby are advised to
OL,8,Fkeep windows and doors closed if
OL,9,Faffected. Please do not travel to the
OL,10,Farea and avoid blocking access routes
OL,11,Fneeded by emergency vehicles. Further
OL,12,Fupdates will be provided as more
OL,13,Finformation becomes available."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
